# Habistat Core Project Rules

## Tech Stack & Standards

- **Framework**: SvelteKit v2 (Svelte v5) with TypeScript and Tauri v2
- **Package Manager**: `pnpm` exclusively - no npm or yarn
- **UI**: TailwindCSS v4 + shadcn-svelte components
- **Database**: SQLite with Drizzle ORM locally, optional Convex cloud sync
- **Auth**: Clerk for authentication
- **Code Style**:
  - 2 spaces indentation
  - Max 100 chars per line
  - Double quotes
  - Semicolons required
  - TypeScript strict mode
  - Components in PascalCase
  - Files in kebab-case
  - Variables/functions in camelCase